variable number	equal 2
variable ofreq	equal 1000
variable efreq	equal 1000
variable T      equal 300.0
variable rhos   equal 0.2
variable nsteps equal 10000

units real

dimension 3

newton on

boundary  p p p

atom_style hybrid bond ellipsoid oxdna
